message.body: Hi Jane - are you free tomorrow and/or Thursday at all to come wrap dollar? I can't get here til later in the evening those days and he has to wait for a wrap to go out.
What time do they go out?
Yes,I can stop there today,around 5:15, not sure about tomorrow but probably yes:)
Great, thank you! There's a paper bag by my trunk with diapers, vetrap, etc. I used all my tape but I think there was lots with your stuff :)
Cute Brenna. Wrapped him before I got here:)
Oh, she's early today! Sorry you wasted a trip.
No,I was going by,not a problem.
